<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Issue Assignment</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .issue-box { background: white; border: 2px solid #667eea; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #667eea; color: white !important; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You've Been Assigned to an Issue ðŸ“‹</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{assigneeName}}!</h2>
            <p><strong>{{assignedBy}}</strong> has assigned you to an issue:</p>
            <div class="issue-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #667eea;">{{issueKey}}</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0;"><strong>{{issueTitle}}</strong></p>
            </div>
            <a href="{{issueUrl}}" class="button">View Issue Details</a>
            <p>Click the button above to view the full details and start working on this issue.</p>
            <p><strong>The GodJira Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 GodJira. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
